### 회원가입(HOST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@#",
  "nickName": "Beemo",
  "phoneNumber": "010-1234-5678"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("userId", response.body.data.userId);
%}


### 0. HOST 로그인 (기존에 회원가입 되어 있다고 가정)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@#"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("hostAccessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 1-1. 첫 페이지 (keyword 없음)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/groups?size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{hostAccessToken}}

> {%
  const nextCursor = response.body.data.nextCursor;
  if (nextCursor !== null && nextCursor !== undefined) {
    client.global.set("cursor_noKeyword_page1", nextCursor);
    console.log("Next cursor (noKeyword, page1):", nextCursor);
  } else {
    console.log("No more pages after PAGE 1 (noKeyword).");
  }
%}

### 1-2. 두 번째 페이지 (keyword 없음): 1-1 실행 결과 nextCursor가 있을 때만 의미 있음
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/groups?size=5&cursor={{cursor_noKeyword_page1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{hostAccessToken}}

> {%
  const data = response.body.data;
  console.log("=== [NO KEYWORD] PAGE 2 ITEMS ===");
  console.log(data.items);

  const nextCursor = data.nextCursor;
  if (nextCursor !== null && nextCursor !== undefined) {
    client.global.set("cursor_noKeyword_page2", nextCursor);
    console.log("Next cursor (noKeyword, page2):", nextCursor);
  } else {
    console.log("No more pages after PAGE 2 (noKeyword).");
  }
%}

